snippet.title: Amber Heard To Get More Screen-Time As Mera In Aquaman 2? | Small Screen Stories
snippet.description:
Welcome to today's episode of Small Screen Stories! On the show today: Amber Heard could be getting more scree-time in Aquaman 2, WB wants a 'Timothee-Chalamet-type' for Terry McGinnis in Batman Beyond and David Fincher signs a four-year exclusive deal with Netflix.
